{"id":21,"parent_id":4,"book_id":4,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":21,"title":"D&C 17","subtitle":"","short_title":"D&C","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/17","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Section 17"],[".studyIntro",["i","Revelation given through Joseph Smith the Prophet to Oliver Cowdery, David Whitmer, and Martin Harris, at Fayette, New York, June 1829, prior to their viewing the engraved plates that contained the Book of Mormon record. Joseph and his scribe, Oliver Cowdery, had learned from the translation of the Book of Mormon plates that three special witnesses would be designated (see",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/ether/5.2-4"},"Ether 5:2–4"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/11.3"},"2 Nephi 11:3"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/27.12"},"27:12"],"). Oliver Cowdery, David Whitmer, and Martin Harris were moved upon by an inspired desire to be the three special witnesses. The Prophet inquired of the Lord, and this revelation was given in answer through the Urim and Thummim."]],[".studySummary",["i",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/17.1-4"},"1–4"],", By faith the Three Witnesses will see the plates and other sacred items;",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/17.5-9"},"5–9"],", Christ bears testimony of the divinity of the Book of Mormon."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/17.1","order":"06.05.017.1950"},["b","1"],"Behold, I say unto you, that you must rely upon my word, which if you do with full purpose of heart, you shall have a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"view"],"of the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_1b"},"plates"],", and also of the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_1c"},"breastplate"],", the",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_1d"},"sword"],"of Laban, the",["sup","e"],["a",{"href":"fn_1e"},"Urim and Thummim"],", which were given to the",["sup","f"],["a",{"href":"fn_1f"},"brother of Jared"],"upon the mount, when he talked with the Lord",["sup","g"],["a",{"href":"fn_1g"},"face to face"],", and the",["sup","h"],["a",{"href":"fn_1h"},"miraculous"],"directors which were given to Lehi while in the wilderness, on the borders of the",["sup","i"],["a",{"href":"fn_1i"},"Red Sea"],"."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/17.2","order":"06.05.017.1951"},["b","2"],"And it is by your faith that you shall obtain a view of them, even by that faith which was had by the prophets of old."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/17.3","order":"06.05.017.1952"},["b","3"],"And after that you have obtained faith, and have seen them with your eyes, you shall",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"testify"],"of them, by the power of God;"],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/17.4","order":"06.05.017.1953"},["b","4"],"And this you shall do that my servant Joseph Smith, Jun., may not be destroyed, that I may bring about my righteous purposes unto the children of men in this work."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/17.5","order":"06.05.017.1954"},["b","5"],"And ye shall testify that you have seen them, even as my servant Joseph Smith, Jun., has seen them; for it is by my power that he has seen them, and it is because he had faith."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/17.6","order":"06.05.017.1955"},["b","6"],"And he has translated the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"book"],", even that",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_6b"},"part"],"which I have commanded him, and as your Lord and your God liveth it is true."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/17.7","order":"06.05.017.1956"},["b","7"],"Wherefore, you have received the same power, and the same faith, and the same gift like unto him;"],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/17.8","order":"06.05.017.1957"},["b","8"],"And if you do these last",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"commandments"],"of mine, which I have given you, the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_8b"},"gates"],"of hell shall not prevail against you; for my",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_8c"},"grace"],"is sufficient for you, and you shall be",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_8d"},"lifted up"],"at the last day."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/17.9","order":"06.05.017.1958"},["b","9"],"And I, Jesus Christ, your",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"Lord"],"and your God, have spoken it unto you, that I might bring about my righteous purposes unto the children of men. Amen."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/17.1a","order":"06.05.017.1959"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/27.12"},"2 Ne. 27:12"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/ether/5.4.2-4"},"Ether 5:4 (2–4)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/5.15.15,24"},"D&C 5:15 (15, 24)"],". See also “",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/three"},"The Testimony of Three Witnesses"],"” in the preliminary pages of the Book of Mormon."],["div",{"id":"1b","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/17.1b","order":"06.05.017.1961"},["b","1b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/morm/6.6"},"Morm. 6:6"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/ether/4.5.4-7"},"Ether 4:5 (4–7)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/pgp/js-h/1.52"},"JS—H 1:52"],"."],["div",{"id":"1c","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/17.1c","order":"06.05.017.1963"},["b","1c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ex/25.7"},"Ex. 25:7"],"."],["div",{"id":"1d","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/17.1d","order":"06.05.017.1965"},["b","1d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/4.9"},"1 Ne. 4:9"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/5.14"},"2 Ne. 5:14"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/jacob/1.10"},"Jacob 1:10"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/1.16"},"Mosiah 1:16"],"."],["div",{"id":"1e","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/17.1e","order":"06.05.017.1967"},["b","1e"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/urim-and-thummim"},"TG Urim and Thummim"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bd/urim-and-thummim"},"BD Urim and Thummim"],"."],["div",{"id":"1f","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/17.1f","order":"06.05.017.1969"},["b","1f"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/ether/3.28.1-28"},"Ether 3:28 (1–28)"],"."],["div",{"id":"1g","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/17.1g","order":"06.05.017.1971"},["b","1g"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/gen/32.30"},"Gen. 32:30"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/num/12.8"},"Num. 12:8"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/pgp/moses/1.2"},"Moses 1:2"],"."],["div",{"id":"1h","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/17.1h","order":"06.05.017.1973"},["b","1h"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/16.16.10,16,26"},"1 Ne. 16:16 (10, 16, 26)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/18.12.12,21"},"18:12 (12, 21)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/5.12"},"2 Ne. 5:12"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/37.38.38-47"},"Alma 37:38 (38–47)"],"."],["div",{"id":"1i","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/17.1i","order":"06.05.017.1975"},["b","1i"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/2.5"},"1 Ne. 2:5"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/17.3a","order":"06.05.017.1977"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/ether/5.3.3-4"},"Ether 5:3 (3–4)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/5.11"},"D&C 5:11"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/witness"},"TG Witness"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/17.6a","order":"06.05.017.1979"},["b","6a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/book-of-mormon"},"TG Book of Mormon"],"."],["div",{"id":"6b","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/17.6b","order":"06.05.017.1981"},["b","6b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/27.8.7-11,21"},"2 Ne. 27:8 (7–11, 21)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/26.9.7-12,18"},"3 Ne. 26:9 (7–12, 18)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/ether/4.5.4-7"},"Ether 4:5 (4–7)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/ether/5.1"},"5:1"],"."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/17.8a","order":"06.05.017.1983"},["b","8a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/19.13"},"D&C 19:13"],"."],["div",{"id":"8b","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/17.8b","order":"06.05.017.1985"},["b","8b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/16.18"},"Matt. 16:18"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/22.26"},"1 Ne. 22:26"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/48.17.16-17"},"Alma 48:17 (16–17)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/11.39.39-40"},"3 Ne. 11:39 (39–40)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/10.69"},"D&C 10:69"],"."],["div",{"id":"8c","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/17.8c","order":"06.05.017.1987"},["b","8c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/grace"},"TG Grace"],"."],["div",{"id":"8d","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/17.8d","order":"06.05.017.1989"},["b","8d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/13.37"},"1 Ne. 13:37"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/27.14.14-15,22"},"3 Ne. 27:14 (14–15, 22)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/5.35"},"D&C 5:35"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/9.14"},"9:14"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/27.18"},"27:18"],"."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/17.9a","order":"06.05.017.1991"},["b","9a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-lord"},"TG Jesus Christ, Lord"],"."]]}
